routeFacts.name: Horseshoe Curve
routeFacts.description: Horseshoe Curve is a US Freight route developed by Skyhook Games, this route runs 40 miles between Altoona and Johnstown, Pensylvania, operated by Norfolk Southern. This route includes GE ES44AC and EMD GP38-2, both in Norfolk Southern livery.
routeInfo: The Horseshoe Curve route covers a 40 mile stretch of the Pittsburgh Line, a major artery of the Norfolk Southern network, from Altoona to Johnstown. The route is named after the famous Horseshoe Curve located just outside of Altoona.
